  "title": "Rich Fluffy Malaysian Pumpkin Curry",
  "description": "A hearty and flavorful Malaysian dish featuring roasted pumpkin in a rich and fluffy curry sauce, finished with a hint of chocolate and a dash of friendly spices.",
